whalebird
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:any of various genera of seabirds which follow ships for food-scraps - <i>Prion</i> spp. (the 1850 and 1862 cits are possibly Prions)
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also dove prion
